<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<strong><a href="./RavenRed">RavenRed</a></strong>: Just a quickie idea, after the death of a promising character through carelessness... Activatable items could maybe be included in the one list, rather than there being separate lists for worn items, and those in the inventory. That way, there is only one list from which to choose, and no need to toggle in between the two lists. <p>
<strong><a href="./MayLith">MayLith</a></strong>: As in, you type shift + a, and a list of activatable items comes up? That'd be nice... 
</p>
